name: Spanky the Fish Who Sucks at Everything - Alpha Build
name_original: Spanky the Fish Who Sucks at Everything - Alpha Build
description:
Spanky the Fish Who Sucks at Everything - Alpha Build is a platformer game developed by Hayden Platt. It came out on 30-03-2020.
Spanky the Fish Who Sucks at Everything - Alpha Build is available on PC, macOS and Linux. The game is sold via itch.io.
